headline: American Express Co (AXP) Q2 2025 Earnings Call Highlights: Record Revenue and Strong EPS ...
summary: American Express Co (AXP) reports a 9% revenue increase and a 17% rise in EPS, reaffirming its financial guidance despite facing competitive pressures and macroeconomic uncertainties.
